Join your fellow Kentico experts, enthusiasts, or anyone who wants to learn about Kentico in Koudekerk aan den Rijn, Netherlands on Monday December 11th.
The group will be covering a variety of topics including sessions for Xperience by Kentico's roadmap, Azure's OpenAI services, and build and deployment pipelines for Kentico projects.
:::note Date: 2023/12/11
Time: 16:00-22:00 CET
Location: 50-B Dorpsstraat 2396 HC Koudekerk aan den Rijn Netherlands :::
Register for the event and see [all the details on Eventbrite](https://www.eventbrite.com/e/tickets-kentico-user-group-benelux-765542427007).
If you would like to see a Kentico user group start in your area, [let us know](https://community.kentico.com/#gridsection-feedback).
